{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/posts/qi9y4f/","result":{"data":{"sitePage":null},"pageContext":{"url":"posts/qi9y4f","relativePath":"posts/qi9y4f","frontmatter":{"title":"AA vs AAA","stackbit_url_path":"posts/qi9y4f","date":"2022-03-25T11:21:55","excerpt":"","tags":[],"categories":[],"template":"post"},"html":"<p><a name=GnquO></a></p>\n<h1>AA</h1>\n<p>前面写了好多关于 Keycloak、Authing 和 IdentityServer 的文章，一般提到它们，人们会用 A&#x26;A 来指代它们。A &#x26; A 是 Authentication &#x26; Authorization 的简称，即鉴权与授权。 比如 Keycloak 就是很多企业采用的一种 A&#x26;A 实施方案。</p>\n<p><a name=Eb5YO></a></p>\n<h1>AAA</h1>\n<p>除了这两A的缩写，还有一个相关的三A的缩写。AAA 是 Authentication、Authorization 和 Accounting 的简称。比如 RADIUS Server 是很多企业采用的一种 AAA 的实施方案。</p>\n<p><a name=uZCWM></a></p>\n<h1>RADIUS</h1>\n<p>这里又来了一个缩写，即 RADIUS，它又是 Remote Authentication Dial-In User Service 的缩写，字面意思是远程认证拨入用户服务。啊，名字有点长又有点绕，通过简称 AAA 服务器，不仅说起来简单，而且 AAA 也的确概括了它所做的事情。</p>\n<p>AAA 服务器使用一种认证协议来授权或者拒绝用户接入一系列的服务，包括 Wi-Fi、VPN 以及各种应用。</p>\n<p><a name=ImVzX></a></p>\n<h2>RADIUS 组件</h2>\n<p>要使用 RADIUS 协议，需要一些组件：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>RADIUS 服务器</li>\n<li>给 RADIUS 用户参考的用户/设备信息目录（也被称为身份提供商或者简称 IDP，又来一缩写）</li>\n<li>RADIUS 客户端</li>\n</ul>\n<p>其中第二个组件是必须的，尽管 RADIUS 服务器会决定一个用户是否可以访问指定的资源，但是它自己本身并不存储用户的凭据或者证书。所以它需要一个目录服务来做检查，这些常用的 IDP 包括了 Active Directory、Azure AD、Google 以及 Okta。\n<a name=fnc5j></a></p>\n<h2>FreeRADIUS</h2>\n<p>FreeRADIUS 是一个开源的 RADIUS 服务器程序，可以安装在 Linux、Unix 和 Windows 上。它的官网 <a href=\"https://freeradius.org/\">https://freeradius.org/</a>  号称 FreeRADIUS 为因特网上三分之一的用户服务：</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 448px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/8c5907b8b7f767e784be67ad4214e726/33b38/1648207076602-9883dbb3-f691-44fb-b3f8-ca5936f230c3.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 102.02702702702702%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block; transition: opacity 0.5s 0.5s; pointer-events: none;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"image.png\"\n        title=\"image.png\"\n        src=\"/static/8c5907b8b7f767e784be67ad4214e726/33b38/1648207076602-9883dbb3-f691-44fb-b3f8-ca5936f230c3.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/8c5907b8b7f767e784be67ad4214e726/12f09/1648207076602-9883dbb3-f691-44fb-b3f8-ca5936f230c3.png 148w,\n/static/8c5907b8b7f767e784be67ad4214e726/e4a3f/1648207076602-9883dbb3-f691-44fb-b3f8-ca5936f230c3.png 295w,\n/static/8c5907b8b7f767e784be67ad4214e726/33b38/1648207076602-9883dbb3-f691-44fb-b3f8-ca5936f230c3.png 448w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 448px) 100vw, 448px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;opacity:0;transition:opacity 0.5s;color:inherit;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p><a name=SaEHB></a></p>\n<h3>本地运行</h3>\n<p>尽管它提供了多种安装方式，但最简单快速的方式应该就是以 Docker 方式运行：\nshell\ndocker run --rm --name my-radius -t -p 1812-1813:1812-1813/udp freeradius/freeradius-server -X</p>\n<p><a name=ZOzdn></a></p>\n<h4>本地测试</h4>\n<p>以上命令以调试方式运行了一个 FreeRADIUS 实例，可以看到更多的日志输出。<br />执行一条命令\nshell\nradtest bob test 127.0.0.1 0 testing123</p>\n<p>即可看到 Docker FreeRADIUS 实例的相关日志输出：<br /><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/70b8f4a63698525a0e70ac0bd4c7f8e3/5a190/1648207286807-09f35008-6eac-4b31-b9fa-906749169aae.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 62.83783783783784%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block; transition: opacity 0.5s 0.5s; pointer-events: none;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"WX20220325-184052.png\"\n        title=\"WX20220325-184052.png\"\n        src=\"/static/70b8f4a63698525a0e70ac0bd4c7f8e3/fcda8/1648207286807-09f35008-6eac-4b31-b9fa-906749169aae.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/70b8f4a63698525a0e70ac0bd4c7f8e3/12f09/1648207286807-09f35008-6eac-4b31-b9fa-906749169aae.png 148w,\n/static/70b8f4a63698525a0e70ac0bd4c7f8e3/e4a3f/1648207286807-09f35008-6eac-4b31-b9fa-906749169aae.png 295w,\n/static/70b8f4a63698525a0e70ac0bd4c7f8e3/fcda8/1648207286807-09f35008-6eac-4b31-b9fa-906749169aae.png 590w,\n/static/70b8f4a63698525a0e70ac0bd4c7f8e3/5a190/1648207286807-09f35008-6eac-4b31-b9fa-906749169aae.png 800w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;opacity:0;transition:opacity 0.5s;color:inherit;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>","pages":[],"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Jeff Tian","author":"@zizhujy","description":"A wild full stack developer","palette":"yellow","header":{"title":"Jeff Tian","tagline":"A wild developer","logo_img":"https://images.ctfassets.net/qixg1o8tujmf/7z1ua3nTOC5B7DwwzAki8I/4e1a05f8db770c285a492eeb1eaa398f/imageedit_3_2509022194.png","background_img":"https://images.ctfassets.net/qixg1o8tujmf/7m0jrKYaDBwEvlc5lo8nt6/6d50a5050d9cdc0d4d2047e35feac292/10648733_696750647079056_2800539603462658695_o.jpg","has_nav":true,"nav_links":[{"label":"Home","url":"/","style":"link","type":"action"},{"label":"About","url":"/about","style":"link","type":"action"},{"label":"关于","url":"https://ggyy.pa-pa.me/about","style":"link","icon_class":"lorem-ipsum","new_wind